      <description>Reverend Charles T. Smith graduated from McKinley High School in 1948. He
            attended Southern University and the New Orleans Baptist Theological Seminary and
            received his Doctor of Divinity from Union Baptist Theological Seminary. He serves as
            the pastor of Shiloh Missionary Baptist Church in Baton Rouge.</description>
